{"tid":804354,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"學術界應否界定， 可信科學 和 傳疑科學呢","createTime":"2018-09-03T03:15:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T11:25:13.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"041c6c0bdc2f33617010585acaa82830f6aab980","tid":804354,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T03:15:22.000Z","msg":"歷史學一般認為：<br />\n人類歷史中，3000年內有文獻記錄的，係信史。其餘幾十億年的歷史，都屬於傳疑年代。<br />\n<br />\n科學又認否界定，可信科學，傳疑科學呢<br />\n<br />\n例如1000光年以外的宇宙，地球內核結構，宇宙爆炸及演化，生命演化等，冇人也冇機器可以親自經驗的科學，係傳疑科學？"},{"pid":"a8f15799b59819ccaf15ddf90df60362c01c5343","tid":804354,"uid":72909,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T03:19:52.000Z","msg":"估下先，你係MrJoe？"},{"pid":"ee2fa385d6ccf5a7fdbb95fbb5cf651c153b31c8","tid":804354,"uid":51021,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8f15799b59819ccaf15ddf90df60362c01c5343","tid":804354,"uid":72909,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T03:19:52.000Z","msg":"估下先，你係MrJoe？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T03:40:51.000Z","msg":"睇行文就知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b3ec1cc96de9cd624d00a3dbb0df11d9a980c5c","tid":804354,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:03:00.000Z","msg":"冇人正經討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e7beb972d78f149a27c9a8f42aecf840903dc93","tid":804354,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:43:21.000Z","msg":"唔明"},{"pid":"9880396bcb125e2579e8c0d237ae0990a45eda45","tid":804354,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e7beb972d78f149a27c9a8f42aecf840903dc93","tid":804354,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:43:21.000Z","msg":"唔明"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:46:59.000Z","msg":"即係有些科學<br />\n證據很強，係定律<br />\n證據中等，係理論<br />\n但有些證據弱的，應否叫「傳疑科學」<br />\n<br />\nEg 宇宙大爆炸論，生命進化史，地核結構，100光